By Metal on Monday, January 3, 2011 - 04:20 pm:

If anyone's interested in the names of these moves they are:
1. Ear Slap 2. Licking 3. Sneeze 4. Charge 5. Bowbow 6. Stamping 7. Roll Press 8. Vacuum 9. Playing 10. Sleeping 11. Uproaring.
Also they chose to localize the special effects of Vacuum as Drain Life instead of Life Drain and of Sleeping as Gain Life instead of Life Heal
